  <main class="content">
    <h1>How to Work LOUIS</h1>
    <p>The following guide will help you operate and understand LOUIS.</p>

    <!-- Step 1 -->
    <div class="step">
      <h3>Step 1: Power On LOUIS</h3>
      <img src="assets/power-on.jpg" alt="Power on LOUIS">
      <p>On top of the battery, there are two switches. Turn on the switch with the green wire to start.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Step 2 -->
    <div class="step">
      <h3>Step 2: Connect to LouisTheRover</h3>
      <img src="assets/connect.jpg" alt="Connect to LouisTheRover">
      <p>On your controller device of choice, open the wi-fi settings, connect to LouisTheRover, and type in the password (Password:LouisLSU).</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Step 3 -->
    <div class="step">
      <h3>Step 3: Type in the IP Address</h3>
      <img src="assets/ipaddress.jpg" alt="Type in the IP Address">
      <p>On your browser of choice, navigate to the IP address port 5000 of the Jetson Nano, which is 10.42.0.1:5000</p>
    </div>

 <!-- Step 4 -->
    <div class="step">
      <h3>Step 4: Confirm Live Camera Feed</h3>
      <img src="assets/camera.jpg" alt="Confirm Live Camera Feed">
      <p>You should see the controller GUI and have a live camera feed as shown.</p>
    </div>

 <!-- Step 5 -->
    <div class="step">
      <h3>Step 5: Toggle the Second Switch</h3>
      <img src="assets/switch.jpg" alt="Toggle the Second Switch">
      <p>Then, you can toggle the second switch on the battery, and LOUIS is ready to control! </p>
    </div>

